  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<h2>A Magnetic Personality</h2><p>The Jiton Clan is a clan that hails proudly from the Land of Wind. Every Kazekage has held this Nature Release and it have brough about an era of prosperity and peace within the Land of Wind. Using Jiton, or Magnet release, a user is usually seen as an extremely oppressive opponent able to fight without lifting a finger a lot of time due to this clan using their Jutsu almost entirely through Chakra control with only a few of their techniques requiring the chakra focusing of handsigns to enable.</p><hr /><h3>Jiton Traits</h3><p><strong>Recommended Ability Score Increase</strong>: +2 Int, +1 Con</p><p><strong>Speed</strong>: Your base walking speed is 30 feet.</p><p><strong>Skill Proficiencies</strong>: Ninshou, Survival.</p><p><strong>Magnet Release Affinity</strong>: You begin with either Earth or Wind Release Affinity. (Pick one)</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
